Title: Presto-Tina-O
Writer: Loren Bouchard (created by), Loren Bouchard (developed by), Jim Dauterive (developed by), Kit Boss
Actors: H. Jon Benjamin, Dan Mintz, Eugene Mirman, Larry Murphy
Plot: Tina becomes a magician's assistant in order to get closer to Jimmy Jr., while Bob becomes the victim of a magician's "curse."
